# Implementation Plan - Milestone 2: Customer Support Quality Auditor

The goal is to build a modern, real-time customer support quality auditor using GenAI. Milestone 2 will focus on detailed scoring, sentiment analysis, and a premium UI.

## User Review Required
> [!IMPORTANT]
> - Are there specific "Extra Features" you want for Milestone 2? I'll add multi-language support (Deepgram) and report exports (PDF).
> - For real-time processing, do you want full WebSocket streaming or is "immediate post-recording analysis" sufficient?

## Proposed Changes

### [Backend] Django API (Milestone_2/backend)
- **Transcription**: Enhance Deepgram integration for diarization (Speaker separation) and multi-language support.
- **Analysis**: Use OpenRouter (GPT-4o or Claude 3.5 Sonnet) for detailed quality audit scoring (Empathy, Resolution, Professionalism, Compliance).
- **History Management**: Simple API to fetch previous audit results.

### [Frontend] React App (Milestone_2/frontend)
- **Vite Setup**: Fast, modern frontend architecture.
- **Design System**: Use CSS variables for a premium "Cyberpunk/Minimalist" look (Dark mode, glassmorphism, smooth gradients).
- **Animations**: Framer Motion for entrance/exit animations of results cards.
- **Features**: Drag-and-drop audio upload, real-time transcription display, and interactive charts for sentiment/scoring.

## Verification Plan
### Automated Tests
- Test Deepgram transcription with sample .m4a/.mp3 files.
- Verify OpenRouter returns valid JSON with scoring for various support scenarios.
### Manual Verification
- Upload test audio files and verify the transcription and scoring accuracy in the UI.
- Test responsive layout on different screen sizes.
